BUT I WANT YOU TO UNDERSTAND
THAT THE RISKS ARE MASSIVE.

12:42.132 --> 12:43.433
IF WE'RE NOT USING
THIS PROGRAM

12:43.433 --> 12:45.435
TO SAVE AMERICAN LIVES,
WHY HAVE IT?

12:45.435 --> 12:47.267
CLOCKWORK
WILL BE PERILOUS

12:47.267 --> 12:49.840
AS LONG AS THERE'S
ONLY ONE GABRIEL.

12:49.840 --> 12:51.842
YOU WANT A HUNDRED OF HIM,
A THOUSAND,

12:51.842 --> 12:55.175
THEN THE PROGRAM HAS TO NOT
ONLY CONTINUE TO PROVE ITSELF,

12:55.175 --> 12:57.177
BUT IT MUST ENDURE.

12:57.177 --> 13:00.881
AND BY IT, I MEAN HIM.

13:00.881 --> 13:03.954
I UNDERSTAND.
I HOPE SO.

13:12.392 --> 13:14.064
Gabriel:
YOU STILL DON'T BELIEVE ME

13:14.064 --> 13:15.896
THAT LUTHER VICK
SURVIVED THIS ROOM.

13:15.896 --> 13:18.068
DO YOU NEED
ME TO BELIEVE YOU?

13:18.068 --> 13:19.529
DEFINITELY NOT.

13:19.529 --> 13:22.402
THE "DEFINITELY"
KIND OF GAVE YOU AWAY.

13:22.402 --> 13:23.303
I'M FLATTERED.

13:25.275 --> 13:27.407
NOTHING'S IMPOSSIBLE,
I SUPPOSE.

13:27.407 --> 13:30.240
YOU'D JUST NEED
TO FIND THE DRAIN.

13:30.240 --> 13:33.944
SECRET SERVICE TRAINS US TO LOOK
AT EVERY ROOM AS THOUGH

13:33.944 --> 13:37.217
IT'S FILLED WITH WATER,
METAPHORICALLY SPEAKING.

13:37.217 --> 13:42.222
IF WATER CAN FIND A WAY,
SO CAN A MAN.

13:42.222 --> 13:43.553
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

13:43.553 --> 13:45.555
FINDING THE DRAIN.

13:45.555 --> 13:47.928
TURN THIS THING ON.

13:54.304 --> 13:55.966
[ SIGHS ]

13:58.238 --> 14:00.310
RELAX. THERE'S NO I.V.
IN MY ARM.

14:04.144 --> 14:05.145
[ BEEP ]

14:05.145 --> 14:06.416
[ CLANG ]

14:06.416 --> 14:08.278
YEAH, NOTHING CREEPY
ABOUT THAT.

14:08.278 --> 14:11.922
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

14:17.928 --> 14:19.229
[ FLATLINE ]

14:19.229 --> 14:21.291
GABRIEL! GABRIEL!

14:21.291 --> 14:22.292
GABRIEL!

14:24.234 --> 14:25.936
NOT A BAD-LOOKING CORPSE,
HUH?

14:27.397 --> 14:30.170
WAS THAT CONCERN
I SAW ON YOUR FACE.

14:31.601 --> 14:33.603
[ BEEP, HISS ]
[ SIGHS ]

14:33.603 --> 14:35.145
SO YOU HACKED IT?

14:35.145 --> 14:36.306
SOMEBODY'S CODED IT

14:36.306 --> 14:38.378
SO THE READINGS CAN
BE CONTROLLED REMOTELY.

14:38.378 --> 14:41.912
FOR THE EXECUTION, THEY PROBABLY
USED A SIMPLE TOGGLE SWITCH.

14:41.912 --> 14:45.585
FLIP THE SWITCH,
THERE'S YOUR FLATLINE.

14:45.585 --> 14:49.259
PROBABLY TAKE SIX PEOPLE
TO PULL IT OFF.

14:49.259 --> 14:50.921
YOU COULD DO IT
WITH THREE.

14:50.921 --> 14:53.223
YOU'D NEED THE DOCTOR
WHO EXAMINES THE BODY,

14:53.223 --> 14:54.564
THE DRIVER, WHO WOULD BE
DELIVERING AN EMPTY COFFIN,

14:54.564 --> 14:57.267
AND YOU'D PROBABLY
ALSO NEED

14:57.267 --> 14:59.569
THE GUY WHO LOADS THE DRUGS
INTO THE --
LET'S GO.

15:01.531 --> 15:03.533
WE'RE NOT ALONE.

15:06.376 --> 15:08.378
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

15:08.378 --> 15:10.380
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

15:12.983 --> 15:16.446
I KNOW IT HURTS, DJANGO.

15:16.446 --> 15:18.288
I'M SORRY.

15:18.288 --> 15:20.350
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

15:20.350 --> 15:22.222
ARE YOU
GONNA MAKE US BETTER?

15:22.222 --> 15:26.426
I'M NOT THAT KIND OF DOCTOR,
BUT MY FATHER IS.

15:26.426 --> 15:28.558
SO I'M GONNA PUT THIS
IN A VERY SPECIAL MICROSCOPE

15:28.558 --> 15:32.432
THAT WILL SEND A PICTURE ALL
THE WAY BACK TO HIM IN VIRGINIA.

15:35.435 --> 15:37.367
IT'LL BE OKAY, MOM.

15:37.367 --> 15:39.339
I'LL BE OKAY.

15:40.640 --> 15:43.013
IS YOUR FATHER GOOD
AT WHAT HE DOES?

15:43.013 --> 15:45.315
THERE'S NOBODY BETTER.

15:49.619 --> 15:51.521
THE HIVES ARE
THE VERY FIRST SYMPTOM,

15:51.521 --> 15:54.154
WHICH IS WHY THE LIPID ENVELOPE
ISN'T PRESENT YET.

15:54.154 --> 15:56.026
OKAY, I'M GONNA LOAD
THE TOMOGRAPHIC IMAGE

15:56.026 --> 15:58.288
TAKEN AFTER I APPLIED NEGATIVE
STAINING TO THE VIRION.

15:58.288 --> 16:00.030
GABRIEL WAS RIGHT.

16:00.030 --> 16:03.033
THE EXECUTION MACHINE
WAS RIGGED.

16:03.033 --> 16:06.436
[ CHUCKLES ] HE WAS RIGHT.
HOT DAMN.

16:06.436 --> 16:08.438
HEY, WE COULD WIN A NOBEL,
LILLIAN.

16:08.438 --> 16:10.270
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

16:10.270 --> 16:12.742
IF IT WEREN'T CLASSIFIED,
OF COURSE.

16:12.742 --> 16:14.304
DAD...

16:14.304 --> 16:15.675
DAD, YOU NEED
TO LOOK AT THIS.

16:17.247 --> 16:20.280
OH, MY GOD.

16:20.280 --> 16:23.283
YOU SEE IT, RIGHT?
Lillian: WHAT IS IT?

16:23.283 --> 16:25.615
VIRUSES ARE CLUMSY.

16:25.615 --> 16:27.157
THEY COLONIZE AT RANDOM,

16:27.157 --> 16:29.259
PASS ONLY
THROUGH MEMBRANOUS TISSUE.

16:29.259 --> 16:31.421
BUT THIS ONE'S UNIQUE.

16:31.421 --> 16:33.363
IT TRAVELS
THROUGH THE SWEAT GLANDS,

16:33.363 --> 16:35.525
WHICH MEANS IT IS
ALL OVER THE CARRIER'S SKIN.

16:35.525 --> 16:38.398
HE INFECTS
ANYONE HE TOUCHES.

16:38.398 --> 16:41.371
YET THE VIRUS DOESN'T AFFECT HIM
UNTIL IT CONVERTS,

16:41.371 --> 16:44.234
WHICH COULD TAKE
WEEKS OR MONTHS OR YEARS.

16:44.234 --> 16:47.237
HE MAY NOT EVEN KNOW
HE'S INFECTED.

16:47.237 --> 16:49.439
GOD.

16:49.439 --> 16:52.442
MY LIFE'S WORK
HAS AUGMENTED HUMANITY,

16:52.442 --> 16:55.285
TO TRY AND MAKE HUMANS BETTER,
STRONGER, FASTER, RIGHT?

16:55.285 --> 16:58.718
WELL, THIS VIRUS
WAS ALSO BUILT BY SOMEONE,

16:58.718 --> 17:01.791
BUT FOR
A DIFFERENT REASON.

17:01.791 --> 17:04.624
THEY WANTED TO MAKE A WEAPON
OF A DIFFERENT KIND.

17:04.624 --> 17:07.127
A KILLING MACHINE.

17:09.359 --> 17:12.532
JONES: I don't know
how they know, but they know.

17:12.532 --> 17:16.336
JONES' BANK ACCOUNTS HAD
SOME BIG CASH DEPOSITS LATELY.

17:16.336 --> 17:18.668
IF IT WEREN'T FOR THOSE,
HE'D BE STRAPPED.

17:18.668 --> 17:20.670
PERFECT CANDIDATE
FOR MANIPULATION --

17:20.670 --> 17:22.512
UNDERPAID PRISON GUARD.

17:22.512 --> 17:25.375
You have to do something.
Pull me out or something.

17:25.375 --> 17:27.717
HE'S IN THE PARKING LOT NOW,
HEADING TOWARDS HIS CAR.

17:27.717 --> 17:30.420
MAN: Calm down, friend.
We have it under control.

17:30.420 --> 17:32.252
GUYS, WE STILL DON'T HAVE A LOCK
ON THE OTHER END OF THIS CALL.

17:32.252 --> 17:34.384
We don't know
who he's talking to.

17:34.384 --> 17:36.226
JONES: You don't have
anything under control!

17:36.226 --> 17:37.487
He said he'd protect me!

17:37.487 --> 17:40.230
STILL NO LOCK.
GABRIEL, DO YOU HAVE IT?
NOT YET.

17:40.230 --> 17:42.462
WHY DON'T WE HAVE
A PICTURE ON THIS?
IT'S CLOSED CIRCUIT.

17:42.462 --> 17:45.295
GABRIEL'S ON THE PRISON GROUNDS,
SO HE COULD TAP IT.
I'm not going to prison!

17:45.295 --> 17:47.137
You have to tell him
to do something.

17:47.137 --> 17:50.069
MAN:
We are doing something.

17:56.476 --> 17:58.178
WHAT JUST HAPPENED?

18:00.350 --> 18:01.851
JONES IS DEAD.

18:01.851 --> 18:04.854
AND I KNOW WHY WE WERE HITTING
A ROAD BLOCK ON THAT TRACE.

18:04.854 --> 18:07.387
OUR PRISON GUARD
WAS ON THE PHONE

18:07.387 --> 18:09.289
WITH SOMEONE
FROM THE PENTAGON.

18:15.565 --> 18:16.826
I'VE BEEN SEARCHING
PENTAGON FILES FOREVER
AND COMING UP EMPTY.

18:16.826 --> 18:18.598
NO MENTION OF LUTHER VICK,
THE PRISON DOCTOR,

18:18.598 --> 18:20.870
OR THE DRIVER, ALL OF WHOM
WERE KILLED OVERNIGHT.

18:20.870 --> 18:22.772
SOMEBODY OVER THERE IS
TRYING TO BEAT LUTHER VICK'S
OLD MURDER RECORD.

18:22.772 --> 18:25.635
WELL, LUTHER'S
NOT FINISHED KILLING.

18:25.635 --> 18:28.138
TOM-TOM BENITEZ'S BODY WAS FOUND
IN A PARKING LOT.

18:28.138 --> 18:29.409
WAIT TILL HE FINDS OUT

18:29.409 --> 18:30.740
HE COULD HAVE KILLED HIM
WITH A SIMPLE HANDSHAKE.

18:30.740 --> 18:32.482
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"WAIT TILL HE FINDS OUT"?

18:32.482 --> 18:35.114
CASSIDY THINKS LUTHER PROBABLY
DOESN'T EVEN KNOW HE'S SICK.

18:35.114 --> 18:36.616
MAKES SENSE
THEY WOULDN'T TELL HIM.

18:36.616 --> 18:38.117
THE QUESTION'S WHO?

18:38.117 --> 18:39.419
YOU HAVE A THEORY?

18:39.419 --> 18:40.750
THE DEFENSE DEPARTMENT
CONNECTION

18:40.750 --> 18:42.292
AND THE FACT
THAT THE VIRUS IS MAN-MADE

18:42.292 --> 18:45.255
LEADS TO ONE CONCLUSION --
AN ILLEGAL BIOWEAPON PROJECT.

18:45.255 --> 18:46.896
GO ON.

18:46.896 --> 18:48.898
HOW WOULD YOU TEST A WEAPONIZED
VIRUS ON A HUMAN BEING?

18:48.898 --> 18:51.261
YOU WOULD TEST IT ON SOMEONE
WHO WOULDN'T BE MISSED.

18:51.261 --> 18:53.233
'CAUSE HE'S
SUPPOSEDLY DEAD.

18:53.233 --> 18:55.765
CREMATE THE IMAGINARY BODY,
LEAVING NO EVIDENCE.

18:55.765 --> 18:59.769
PERFECT PLAN.
UNLESS LUTHER ESCAPES AND
YOU HAVE TO CLEAN UP THE MESS.

18:59.769 --> 19:02.372
BUT WHY CAN'T YOU FIND THE FILES
IN THE PENTAGON SYSTEM?

19:02.372 --> 19:05.715
BECAUSE IT'S NOT THE PENTAGON.
IT'S A PRIVATE CONTRACTOR.

19:05.715 --> 19:07.277
AND THERE'S
A LOT OF THEM IN TEXAS.

19:07.277 --> 19:08.578
I'LL WORRY ABOUT THAT.

19:08.578 --> 19:10.850
YOU TWO JUST STAY FOCUSED
ON PATIENT ZERO.

19:10.850 --> 19:12.322
LUANNE VICK'S HOUSE?

19:13.683 --> 19:16.726
в™Є TEARS ON MY PILLOW в™Є

19:16.726 --> 19:20.330
в™Є I'VE GOT ALL NIGHT LONG в™Є

19:22.232 --> 19:24.364
в™Є TEARS ON MY PILLOW в™Є

19:24.364 --> 19:29.799
в™Є I'VE GOT ALL NIGHT LONG в™Є

19:29.799 --> 19:32.542
[ GASPS ]

19:32.542 --> 19:34.374
SHH.

19:34.374 --> 19:36.406
THEY GOT PEOPLE
LOOKING FOR ME.

19:36.406 --> 19:40.750
IF I LET GO, YOU PROMISE
YOU'RE GONNA KEEP IT TOGETHER?

19:40.750 --> 19:43.853
NO SCREAMING? HMM?

19:43.853 --> 19:45.855
[ WHIMPERS ]

19:48.558 --> 19:49.889
WHAT?

19:49.889 --> 19:52.692
WELL, AIN'T YOU GLAD
TO SEE ME?

19:52.692 --> 19:56.195
OF COURSE, BUT H-HOW --
HOW IS THIS EVEN POSSIBLE?

19:56.195 --> 20:01.200
WELL, THE GOVERNMENT'S
TWICE AS BAD AS ME.

20:01.200 --> 20:03.303
BUT ONLY HALF AS SMART.
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:03.303 --> 20:05.635
YOU KNOW, THE LAST THING
I REMEMBER SEEING

20:05.635 --> 20:07.677
WAS YOUR PRETTY FACE
JUST BEFORE I DIED.

20:07.677 --> 20:14.514
AND THEN I WAKE IN SOME KIND
OF LABORATORY OR SOMETHING.

20:14.514 --> 20:18.948
PEOPLE WEARING THESE
WHITE COATS AND DUCK SUITS.

20:18.948 --> 20:20.950
DUCK SUITS?
MM-HMM.

20:20.950 --> 20:22.852
YOU KNOW,
THE RUBBER ONES.

20:22.852 --> 20:26.956
ANYHOW, THEY SHOT ME UP
WITH ALL SORTS OF STUFF.

20:26.956 --> 20:30.800
TOLD ME ONE SHOT WOULD PUT ME
TO SLEEP, BUT LOOK IT.

20:30.800 --> 20:34.233
I GOT THESE BAD VEINS FROM
BOOTING TECATA ALL THOSE YEARS.

20:34.233 --> 20:37.837
[ CHUCKLES ]
SO I PRETENDED I WAS OUT,
WAITED FOR MY CHANCE,

20:37.837 --> 20:39.669
AND WENT
ALL KINDS OF CRAZY.

20:39.669 --> 20:40.970
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

20:40.970 --> 20:43.843
NEXT THING I KNEW,
BREAK OUT OF THE BUILDING,

20:43.843 --> 20:46.846
IN THE MIDDLE OF ONE
OF THEM RICH-KID CONCERTS.

20:49.879 --> 20:52.251
[ GASPS ]

20:52.251 --> 20:54.924
I BEEN IN PRISON,
GIRL.

20:54.924 --> 20:56.956
WE AIN'T SLOW DANCING.

20:56.956 --> 20:59.329
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

21:02.862 --> 21:06.536
WHAT AM I DOING HERE,
LILLIAN?

21:06.536 --> 21:08.368
YOU WANTED
SHARED PRODUCT.

21:08.368 --> 21:09.899
THIS WON'T BE
IN MY SIT-REPORT.

21:09.899 --> 21:12.842
WHAT I'M ABOUT TO TELL YOU
HAS TO REMAIN CONFIDENTIAL.

21:12.842 --> 21:14.844
OF COURSE.

21:14.844 --> 21:17.046
THE VIRUS IS MAN-MADE.

21:17.046 --> 21:18.748
CAN YOU SOURCE IT?

21:18.748 --> 21:20.279
NOT SPECIFICALLY.

21:20.279 --> 21:22.912
BUT GIVEN THE INCUBATION RATE,
WE THINK THAT PATIENT ZERO

21:22.912 --> 21:24.484
WAS INFECTED
WITHIN TWO HOURS

21:24.484 --> 21:26.055
OF HIS APPEARANCE
AT THE FESTIVAL.

21:26.055 --> 21:28.588
SO HE WAS INFECTED
IN THE AUSTIN AREA.

21:28.588 --> 21:29.789
THERE'S MORE.

21:29.789 --> 21:31.891
WE THINK IT'S ONE
OF YOUR CONTRACTORS.

21:31.891 --> 21:33.623
WHY DO YOU THINK THAT?

21:33.623 --> 21:35.965
NOBODY TAKES ON
THE COST AND RISK

21:35.965 --> 21:38.027
OF A BIOWEAPON
WITHOUT A BUYER.

21:38.027 --> 21:39.869
AND THERE'S NO BUYER
LIKE THE MILITARY.

21:39.869 --> 21:41.731
AH, THAT'S CONJECTURE.

21:41.731 --> 21:44.033
DO YOU HAVE ANYTHING
THAT STANDS UP?

21:44.033 --> 21:47.306
WE TRACKED A PHONE CALL
TO A PROTECTED P-2-7 NUMBER.

21:47.306 --> 21:48.738
THE PENTAGON?

21:48.738 --> 21:50.410
SOMEONE IN YOUR SHOP
IS VIOLATING

21:50.410 --> 21:51.941
THE GENEVA CONVENTION,
GREG.

21:51.941 --> 21:54.944
[ SIGHS ]

21:54.944 --> 21:58.648
OKAY, LET ME GET
MY BEAK WET ON THIS.

21:58.648 --> 22:01.821
THANK YOU
FOR COMING TO ME, LILLIAN.

22:01.821 --> 22:03.493
I OWE YOU ONE.

22:09.899 --> 22:11.100
YOU HAVE HIM?

22:11.100 --> 22:14.734
MAKING A CALL NOW.
ROUTING TO YOUR EARPIECE.

22:14.734 --> 22:15.835
GREG:
We need to catch this guy

22:15.835 --> 22:18.508
before Lillian Strand's
people do.

22:18.508 --> 22:20.009
HE TERMINATED THE CALL.

22:20.009 --> 22:22.512
YOU WERE RIGHT.
HE'S DIRTY.

22:22.512 --> 22:23.973
EVER SINCE THE BEGINNING
OF THE IRAQ WAR,

22:23.973 --> 22:25.975
DEFENSE INTELLIGENCE
HAS BEEN OBSESSED

22:25.975 --> 22:27.947
WITH BIO
AND CHEMICAL WEAPONS.

22:27.947 --> 22:29.779
OF COURSE, THIS PHONE CALL
DOESN'T PROVE ANYTHING.

22:29.779 --> 22:31.781
HAD HE MENTIONED LUTHER VICK
BY NAME WE WOULD HAVE HIM.

22:31.781 --> 22:34.854
NO, HE'S TOO SMART
FOR THAT.

22:34.854 --> 22:37.857
Gabriel:
SEE? I'M A NATURAL.

22:37.857 --> 22:40.560
JUST DON'T CRASH.

22:40.560 --> 22:43.633
LOOK. NO HANDS.

22:43.633 --> 22:44.964
OR CRAZY NELSON HAT.

22:44.964 --> 22:48.498
DO YOU SEE ANYONE INSIDE?

22:48.498 --> 22:50.600
[ SIGHS ]
SWITCHING TO THERMAL NOW.

22:52.572 --> 22:54.373
C-Doc,
are you seeing this?

22:54.373 --> 22:56.946
That's Tom-Tom's van
in the driveway,

22:56.946 --> 22:58.377
WHICH LUTHER STOLE.

22:58.377 --> 23:00.550
LET'S GO GET OUR GUY.

23:00.550 --> 23:01.851
ALL RIGHT, TAC TEAM'S
15 MINUTES OUT.

23:01.851 --> 23:04.013
LILLIAN, IF I MAY?

23:04.013 --> 23:06.716
PLEASE REMEMBER
THE ANTIBODIES

23:06.716 --> 23:08.558
CAN ONLY BE HARVESTED
FROM A LIVE VIRUS.

23:08.558 --> 23:11.561
THAT VIRUS WILL DIE
IF THE HOST DIES.

23:11.561 --> 23:13.863
NOTED, DOC.
WE'LL BRING HIM BACK ALIVE.

23:13.863 --> 23:15.865
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?
WE'RE WAITING FOR THE TAC TEAM.

23:15.865 --> 23:17.467
WE CAN'T WAIT.

23:17.467 --> 23:19.869
HEY, YOU DON'T JUST GET TO MAKE
THESE DECISIONS ON YOUR OWN.

23:19.869 --> 23:21.801
WE'RE EITHER PARTNERS
OR WE'RE NOT.

23:21.801 --> 23:23.102
WHO SAID WE'RE PARTNERS?

23:23.102 --> 23:25.575
I HAVE A JOB TO DO, TOO.
AND THAT'S TO KEEP YOU ALIVE.

23:25.575 --> 23:27.577
YOU HEARD
WHAT THE DOC SAID.

23:27.577 --> 23:28.878
DO YOU REALLY WANT TO RISK
THE LOCAL POLICE

23:28.878 --> 23:32.882
PULLING THE TRIGGER ON LUTHER,
A COP KILLER?

23:32.882 --> 23:34.584
FINE.

23:34.584 --> 23:36.716
BUT YOU'RE WEARING THESE.

23:36.716 --> 23:38.718
GLOVES?
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

23:38.718 --> 23:40.189
IF YOU COME INTO DIRECT CONTACT
WITH THE VIRUS,

23:40.189 --> 23:41.551
YOU WILL BE INFECTED.

23:41.551 --> 23:44.554
YEAH, BUT WE'LL HAVE
THE CURE IN HANDCUFFS.

23:44.554 --> 23:46.656
[ SIGHS ]
CAN YOU EVER JUST SAY YES?

23:51.901 --> 23:53.933
YOU CAN'T TOUCH HIM.
UNDERSTAND?

23:53.933 --> 23:55.665
ARE YOU READY?

24:04.844 --> 24:07.146
[ GUNSHOTS ]

24:07.146 --> 24:09.448
DO YOU KNOW
HOW EMASCULATING IT IS

24:09.448 --> 24:10.720
WHEN YOU TACKLE ME
LIKE THAT?

24:13.483 --> 24:14.884
ARE YOU SAYING
YOU FEEL LIKE A GIRL?

24:14.884 --> 24:16.025
THAT'S NOT
WHAT I'M SAYING!

24:18.958 --> 24:20.960
'CAUSE YOU LOOK
PRETTY TODAY.

24:28.538 --> 24:31.771
ONE'S GOING AROUND FRONT.
I GOT THIS ONE.

24:31.771 --> 24:32.972
[ GUNSHOTS ]

24:32.972 --> 24:34.804
GO.

24:47.617 --> 24:49.218
[ GRUNTS ]

25:24.754 --> 25:26.726
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

25:26.726 --> 25:28.998
[ GUNFIRE ]

25:33.633 --> 25:35.034
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

25:40.640 --> 25:43.973
LAST TIME I FELT
A HAMMER STRIKE LIKE THAT

25:43.973 --> 25:45.314
WAS FORT BENNING,
GEORGIA.

25:45.314 --> 25:49.879
SO WE JUST GOT OUR ASSES KICKED
BY U.S. SPECIAL FORCES.

25:54.323 --> 25:55.755
HANG ON A SECOND.
YOU'RE PISSED AT US?

25:55.755 --> 25:57.587
LUTHER VICK IS INFECTED
AND HIGHLY CONTAGIOUS.

25:57.587 --> 25:59.258
YOU TWO SHOULD NEVER HAVE
ENGAGED ON YOUR OWN.

25:59.258 --> 26:01.290
NOT TO MENTION,
YOU DESTROYED MY QUADCOPTER.

26:01.290 --> 26:04.864
WELL, IT WASN'T LUTHER
WE FOUND IN THERE, WAS IT?

26:04.864 --> 26:07.566
THESE WERE SOLDIERS
IN LEVEL-A HAZMAT SUITS,

26:07.566 --> 26:08.738
SPECIAL FORCES TRAINING,

26:08.738 --> 26:11.140
AND COVER FIRE
FROM AN MP5 SUBMACHINE GUN.

26:11.140 --> 26:12.642
WHEN ARE YOU GONNA ARREST
THIS GENERAL OF YOURS?

26:12.642 --> 26:13.743
YOU DON'T JUST ARREST

26:13.743 --> 26:15.004
THE DIRECTOR
OF DEFENSE INTELLIGENCE.

26:15.004 --> 26:16.706
WE NEED PROOF
THAT CARTER'S INVOLVED.

26:16.706 --> 26:18.007
HOW ARE YOU
GONNA GET THAT?

26:18.007 --> 26:19.849
HE'S ARROGANT
AND PROBABLY DOESN'T THINK

26:19.849 --> 26:21.210
HE'S DONE ANYTHING WRONG.

26:21.210 --> 26:23.883
HE'LL MAKE A MISTAKE.
BUT THAT'S MY CONCERN.

26:23.883 --> 26:25.354
YOU JUST STAY ON PROBLEM.

26:25.354 --> 26:28.988
WE CAN'T MAKE A CURE
WITHOUT LUTHER.

26:28.988 --> 26:30.259
[ BEEP ]
WHAT IS IT?

26:32.191 --> 26:34.994
DJANGO, THE KID
FROM THE FESTIVAL.

26:34.994 --> 26:37.166
HIS FATHER JUST DIED.

26:40.770 --> 26:42.772
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

27:08.958 --> 27:11.630
[ AIR HISSES ]
Nelson: NO, DON'T!

27:19.408 --> 27:21.771
WE CAN'T
LET THEM DIE, TOO.

27:28.247 --> 27:31.250
LETTERS.

27:31.250 --> 27:34.153
WHAT ABOUT THEM?

27:35.925 --> 27:38.758
LUANNE AND LUTHER MET
AFTER HE WAS INCARCERATED.

27:38.758 --> 27:39.989
YEAH. SO?

27:39.989 --> 27:42.061
IT'S CALLED HYBRISTOPHILIA --
MONSTER WORSHIP.

27:42.061 --> 27:44.694
THESE WOMEN LIKE TO WRITE
LETTERS TO HORRIBLE MEN.

27:44.694 --> 27:46.395
THOSE LETTERS
CAN TURN INTO VISITS

27:46.395 --> 27:47.997
AND SOMETIMES
A PRISON WEDDING.

27:47.997 --> 27:50.239
IT'S PRISON POLICY TO SCAN ALL
DOCUMENTS RECEIVED BY INMATES.

27:50.239 --> 27:51.440
ANY LETTER LUANNE
WROTE TO LUTHER

27:51.440 --> 27:53.202
WOULD BE KEPT IN A DATABASE.
I'M ALREADY IN.

27:53.202 --> 27:56.045
SCAN FOR PLACES -- HOMES,
HOTELS, VACATION SPOTS.

27:56.045 --> 27:58.307
HERE'S SOMETHING.

27:58.307 --> 28:01.150
LUANNE WROTE ABOUT A FARMHOUSE
HER GRANDMOTHER OWNED.

28:01.150 --> 28:03.252
"SHE'S GONNA LEAVE IT
TO ME IN HER WILL."

28:03.252 --> 28:05.184
HOW QUICKLY CAN YOU --
GRANDMOTHER, SELMA GREEN.

28:05.184 --> 28:08.187
SHE'S IN A RETIREMENT HOME
BUT STILL OWNS THE HOUSE.

28:08.187 --> 28:11.390
ROUTE 35 NORTH,
OUTSIDE OF ROUND ROCK.

28:15.164 --> 28:16.826
Woman:
LATEST REPORTS INDICATE

28:16.826 --> 28:19.769
THAT THE DEATH COUNT
HAS REACHED 183.

28:19.769 --> 28:22.401
SYMPTOMS BEGIN
WITH HIVES ON THE TORSO

28:22.401 --> 28:24.974
FOLLOWED BY HIGH FEVER
AND MUSCLE PAIN.

28:24.974 --> 28:28.177
[ DOOR OPENS ]
IF YOU OBSERVE ANY OF THESE
SYMPTOMS ON YOURSELF...

28:28.177 --> 28:32.341
I GOT BEER, CIGARETTES,
SOME CHIPS AND STUFF.

28:32.341 --> 28:34.944
I DON'T THINK WE'RE GONNA SCORE
IN THIS TOWN, THOUGH.

28:34.944 --> 28:37.446
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

28:37.446 --> 28:40.119
THIS IS A LOT BETTER
THAN STARING

28:40.119 --> 28:41.420
AT THOSE PICTURES
YOU USED TO SEND.

28:41.420 --> 28:43.422
THOSE PICTURES WERE NICE.

28:43.422 --> 28:46.155
[ CHUCKLES ]
MM.

28:46.155 --> 28:48.027
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:51.360 --> 28:53.032
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:53.032 --> 28:55.364
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

28:55.364 --> 28:56.465
WHAT'S WRONG?

28:56.465 --> 28:58.367
GET OFF!
WHAT?

28:58.367 --> 29:00.409
AAH!
[ CLATTER ]

29:00.409 --> 29:01.811
YOU GOT IT!

29:01.811 --> 29:03.913
T-T-THAT DISEASE
THEY'VE BEEN TALKING ABOUT!

29:03.913 --> 29:05.014
OH, GOD! OH, GOD!
WHAT DO I DO?

29:05.014 --> 29:06.245
WHAT DO THEY --
WHAT DO THEY SAY TO DO?

29:06.245 --> 29:07.346
I-I NEED A DOCTOR.

29:07.346 --> 29:09.378
I NEED -- I NEED
TO GO TO THE HOSPITAL!

29:09.378 --> 29:10.880
I NEED --

29:12.351 --> 29:15.424
WAIT A MINUTE.

29:15.424 --> 29:16.926
THAT'S WHAT
THEY DID TO YOU.

29:16.926 --> 29:18.357
WHAT ARE
YOU TALKING ABOUT?

29:18.357 --> 29:20.389
YOU SAID THAT
THEY TOOK YOU SOMEWHERE

29:20.389 --> 29:21.831
AND SHOT YOU UP
WITH ALL KINDS OF STUFF.

29:21.831 --> 29:23.362
MAYBE THEY MADE YOU SICK!

29:23.362 --> 29:24.763
MAYBE YOU'RE THE ONE WHO'S
GIVING IT ALL TO THESE PEOPLE!

29:24.763 --> 29:26.765
NO, NO. YOU'RE CRAZY.
LOOK AT -- LOOK AT ME.

29:26.765 --> 29:27.997
I'M -- I'M -- I'M FINE.

29:27.997 --> 29:30.199
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
I'VE BEEN AROUND, LUTHER!

29:34.103 --> 29:36.275
I CAN'T TAKE YOU
TO THE HOSPITAL, GIRL.

29:38.247 --> 29:40.449
I CAN'T TAKE YOU ALONG
IN THAT CONDITION.

29:42.781 --> 29:46.115
AND I CAN'T LEAVE YOU HERE
TO LEAD THEM TO ME.

29:51.390 --> 29:53.562
300 NEW CASES TODAY.

29:53.562 --> 29:58.267
THIS IS WHAT HAPPENS WHEN YOU
SCREW AROUND WITH MOTHER NATURE.

29:58.267 --> 30:01.230
I DIDN'T MEAN YOU,
OBVIOUSLY.

30:01.230 --> 30:03.572
KNOW HOW MANY PEOPLE THEY TRIED
TO IMPLANT THE CHIP IN

30:03.572 --> 30:05.234
BEFORE I CAME ALONG?

30:05.234 --> 30:08.407
THREE.
ALL VOLUNTEERS, LIKE ME.

30:08.407 --> 30:10.539
WHAT HAPPENED TO THEM?

30:10.539 --> 30:13.582
TWO DEAD,
ONE PARALYZED.

30:13.582 --> 30:16.415
I'M SURPRISED
YOU VOLUNTEERED AFTER THAT.

30:16.415 --> 30:18.948
COULDN'T FIND AMELIA.

30:18.948 --> 30:20.219
I THOUGHT
THE CHIP WOULD HELP.

30:23.322 --> 30:25.354
[ SIGHS ]

30:25.354 --> 30:26.495
LET'S GO.

30:31.260 --> 30:34.303
GLOVES.

30:34.303 --> 30:37.436
PUT...THEM...ON.

30:37.436 --> 30:40.970
[ SIGHS ]

30:53.352 --> 30:54.423
GABRIEL.

31:03.432 --> 31:06.435
BLOOD'S STILL BLOOMING.
IT'S FRESH. MEANS HE'S CLOSE.

31:06.435 --> 31:09.398
[ SWING CREAKING ]

32:00.319 --> 32:01.620
[ GUN COCKS ]
DROP IT.

32:05.094 --> 32:08.297
GOOD GIRL.
LET HER GO, LUTHER.
WE DON'T WANT TO HURT YOU.

32:08.297 --> 32:11.160
HURT ME? AND HOW YOU PLAN
ON DOING THAT?

32:12.401 --> 32:15.664
WHAT'S WITH THE GLOVES?

32:15.664 --> 32:17.436
[ GRUNTS ]

32:18.637 --> 32:20.409
STAY BACK, GABRIEL.

32:20.409 --> 32:22.341
SCUMBAG INFECTED ME.

32:22.341 --> 32:24.443
INFECTED YOU?

32:24.443 --> 32:26.415
YOU'RE TELLING ME
LUANNE WAS RIGHT?

32:26.415 --> 32:28.417
I WAS A CARRIER?

32:28.417 --> 32:29.478
WHAT DO WE HAVE?

32:29.478 --> 32:31.350
WE'VE GOT GENERAL CARTER
ON A SAT PHONE.

32:31.350 --> 32:32.481
TRIANGULATING NOW.

32:32.481 --> 32:34.423
[ BEEPING ]

32:34.423 --> 32:35.524
GOT IT.

32:35.524 --> 32:37.386
RECIPIENT OF THE CALL
IS TWO CLICKS AWAY

32:37.386 --> 32:38.487
FROM GABRIEL AND RILEY'S
CURRENT LOCATION.

32:38.487 --> 32:41.060
ON SPEAKER NOW.

32:41.060 --> 32:42.491
GREG: You are authorized
for containment.

32:42.491 --> 32:45.034
All solutions are go.
Repeat.

32:45.034 --> 32:46.195
All solutions are go.

32:46.195 --> 32:48.367
THEY KNOW WHERE LUTHER IS.
GET ME GABRIEL.

32:48.367 --> 32:49.498
LILLIAN, WE GOT HIM.

32:49.498 --> 32:51.600
WE NEED AN EXFIL CHOPPER
AT THIS LOCATION.

32:53.302 --> 32:55.404
AND MAKE IT QUICK.

32:58.647 --> 33:00.279
GABRIEL, CARTER'S MEN
ARE CLOSING IN.

33:00.279 --> 33:03.082
WE GOT TO MOVE.

33:03.082 --> 33:04.313
MAN:
We're on site, sir.

33:04.313 --> 33:05.484
GREG:
Approach and detain.

33:05.484 --> 33:07.716
GABRIEL,
GET OUT OF THERE.

33:07.716 --> 33:10.459
[ GUN COCKS ]
DON'T MOVE!

33:10.459 --> 33:12.161
LET ME SEE THOSE HANDS!

33:12.161 --> 33:15.424
DROP YOUR WEAPON!
WEAPONS DOWN!

33:15.424 --> 33:19.568
[ SIGHS ]
WELL, THAT WAS FAST.

33:19.568 --> 33:24.103
Sir, we've secured the package.
Collateral snug and tight.

33:27.076 --> 33:29.508
PACKAGE TO THE KITCHEN.

33:29.508 --> 33:31.510
SCRUB THE COLLATERAL.

33:31.510 --> 33:33.382
YES, SIR.

33:33.382 --> 33:36.215
All right, let's go. Move.
Get them inside.

33:36.215 --> 33:40.319
LET'S GO. INSIDE.

33:51.400 --> 33:53.262
[ GRUNTS ]

33:54.133 --> 33:56.205
YOU OKAY?
YEAH.

33:56.205 --> 33:57.466
DON'T GET TOO CLOSE.

33:57.466 --> 33:58.337
[ SIGHS ]

33:59.708 --> 34:02.211
[ SIGHS ]

34:02.211 --> 34:05.474
I DON'T GET IT.
WHY DIDN'T THEY JUST SHOOT US?

34:05.474 --> 34:07.776
'CAUSE THEY DON'T WANT TO LEAVE
ANY BULLETS BEHIND IN THE ASHES.

34:07.776 --> 34:09.148
Man: TORCH IT.

34:09.148 --> 34:11.150
[ FLAMES ROAR ]

34:24.793 --> 34:25.794
[ COUGHS ]

34:25.794 --> 34:27.636
[ COUGHS ]

34:27.636 --> 34:29.268
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

34:29.268 --> 34:30.669
THE DRAIN.

34:30.669 --> 34:32.801
THE WOOD'S WEAKER WHERE THE
FLAMES ARE. THAT'S THE WAY OUT.

34:32.801 --> 34:35.544
LET'S DO IT.

34:37.776 --> 34:39.178
THERE'S A GUY OUTSIDE
MAKING SURE WE DON'T GET OUT.

34:39.178 --> 34:41.110
[ COUGHS ]
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

34:41.110 --> 34:42.511
I'M INSIDE HIS HELMET CAM.

34:42.511 --> 34:44.513
COME ON.
WE GOT TO DO THIS TOGETHER.

34:44.513 --> 34:46.185
YOU TOUCH ME,
AND YOU'RE INFECTED.

34:46.185 --> 34:49.388
WE'RE EITHER PARTNERS
OR WE'RE NOT.

34:49.388 --> 34:51.560
COME ON.

34:56.495 --> 34:59.668
ARE YOU READY?

34:59.668 --> 35:01.430
ONE, TWO...

35:21.490 --> 35:22.621
I'M IN
THE OTHER GUY'S COMM.

35:22.621 --> 35:24.223
I CAN SEE
EVERYTHING HE SEES.

35:24.223 --> 35:25.554
WHERE IS LUTHER?

35:25.554 --> 35:26.855
HALF A CLICK TO THE NORTH,
HEADING TOWARDS THE ROAD.

35:26.855 --> 35:28.457
WE CAN STILL CATCH THEM.

35:43.242 --> 35:45.174
[ GRUNTS ]

35:56.255 --> 35:57.256
[ GUN COCKS ]

36:00.429 --> 36:03.562
GABRIEL...BEHIND YOU.

36:06.635 --> 36:08.367
YOU DON'T WANT TO DO THAT,
LUTHER.

36:08.367 --> 36:10.499
YOU THINK THIS
IS A FIRST FOR ME?

36:10.499 --> 36:11.940
I'VE OFFED COPS BEFORE.

36:11.940 --> 36:13.702
WE'RE TRYING
TO SAVE YOU, MAN.

36:13.702 --> 36:17.175
SAVE ME? TURN AROUND.

36:17.175 --> 36:19.378
[ SIGHS ]
IF YOU SAY SO.

36:23.352 --> 36:26.755
AH. WE'RE IN QUITE
THE PICKLE NOW, BOY.

36:26.755 --> 36:28.487
THE GUN IS AT YOUR THROAT,
LUTHER.

36:28.487 --> 36:29.958
CAREFUL, GABRIEL.

36:29.958 --> 36:32.491
YEAH, I KNOW.

36:32.491 --> 36:34.793
I'M SMART ENOUGH TO KNOW
THAT PEOPLE NEED ME ALIVE.

36:34.793 --> 36:36.625
THIS SICKNESS
I SUPPOSEDLY HAVE --

36:36.625 --> 36:38.327
IT HAS SOMETHING TO DO
WITH THAT, RIGHT?

36:38.327 --> 36:42.331
RIGHT.
WELL, AM I GETTING YOU SICK
RIGHT NOW?

36:42.331 --> 36:45.504
HOW DOES THIS WORK?
YOU KILL ANYONE YOU TOUCH.

36:45.504 --> 36:46.905
YOU SHOULD
BE USED TO THAT.

36:49.638 --> 36:50.779
WHAT ARE YOU DOING,
LUTHER?

36:50.779 --> 36:52.981
THIS WORLD
NEVER GAVE ME NOTHING.

36:52.981 --> 36:54.513
SO, WE'RE EVEN.

36:54.513 --> 36:55.714
LUTHER, DON'T!

36:55.714 --> 36:57.986
OH, DON'T WORRY.
I'M GONNA REACH UP FROM HELL

36:57.986 --> 36:59.588
AND PULL BOTH OF YOU
DOWN WITH ME.

37:01.820 --> 37:05.294
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

37:08.697 --> 37:11.229
WE GOT TO GET HIM
TO CDC HQ.

37:11.229 --> 37:12.931
YOU TOO.
YOU NEED THAT VACCINE.

37:16.605 --> 37:20.269
WE LOST BOTH OF THEM?
WHERE'S LUTHER?!

37:20.269 --> 37:22.240
SOMEBODY TELL ME SOMETHING!
[ EXPLOSION ]

37:22.240 --> 37:24.343
GO! GO! GO! GO! GO!

37:24.343 --> 37:26.014
GET ON THE GROUND NOW!
GET THOSE HANDS UP!

37:26.014 --> 37:28.547
WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON HERE?

37:28.547 --> 37:30.349
DO YOU KNOW WHO I AM?

37:30.349 --> 37:32.651
YES, GENERAL,
WE KNOW WHO YOU ARE.

37:32.651 --> 37:34.283
WE KNOW NOW.

37:35.684 --> 37:38.727
SO THIS IS WHAT THEY MEAN
BY CIVILIAN LEADERSHIP.

37:38.727 --> 37:40.329
YOU TWO?

37:40.329 --> 37:41.990
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

37:41.990 --> 37:43.962
YOU USED A HUMAN BEING
AS A GUINEA PIG.

37:43.962 --> 37:45.994
NO MATTER WHAT HIS CRIME --
HUMAN BEING?

37:45.994 --> 37:48.567
LUTHER VICK KILLED
TWO POLICE OFFICERS.

37:48.567 --> 37:50.699
IN RETURN,
THE COURT TOOK AWAY HIS LIFE

37:50.699 --> 37:52.471
AND GAVE IT TO THE STATE.

37:52.471 --> 37:53.642
WE ARE THE STATE.

37:53.642 --> 37:56.745
YOU'RE JUST AS BAD
AS THE MURDERER YOU USED.

37:56.745 --> 37:59.578
IF WE CAN MAKE AN ANTI-VIRUS
OUT OF LUTHER'S BLOOD,

37:59.578 --> 38:01.610
WE'LL BE READY
WHEN A WEAPON LIKE THIS VIRUS

38:01.610 --> 38:03.352
COMES ACROSS OUR BORDERS.

38:03.352 --> 38:05.354
WE BOTH KNOW
IT'S ON THE WAY.

38:05.354 --> 38:07.616
THE MONSTERS ARE AT THE GATE,
LILLIAN.

38:07.616 --> 38:10.589
LOOKS TO ME LIKE THE MONSTERS
ARE RIGHT HERE.

38:12.421 --> 38:13.862
GET HIM OUT OF HERE.

38:17.426 --> 38:20.499
THAT'S A BIG WIN FOR YOU.

38:20.499 --> 38:23.732
IT'S A WIN
FOR THE COUNTRY.

38:23.732 --> 38:26.405
YOU'VE EXPANDED
THE PURVIEW OF CYBER COM

38:26.405 --> 38:28.577
DRAMATICALLY
WITH CLOCKWORK.

38:28.577 --> 38:32.581
YOU KNOW, THE ONLY THING
THAT WORRIES ME

38:32.581 --> 38:34.943
MORE THAN THE POWER
OF ANY ONE AGENCY

38:34.943 --> 38:37.916
IS THE POWER OF
ANY ONE AGENT.

38:37.916 --> 38:40.389
ARE WE TALKING
ABOUT GABRIEL?

38:40.389 --> 38:42.521
OR ARE WE TALKING
ABOUT ME?

39:02.711 --> 39:04.673
THAT REALLY GONNA WORK?

39:04.673 --> 39:06.545
THE ANTI-VIRUS?

39:06.545 --> 39:08.547
YEAH.

39:08.547 --> 39:11.019
TAKE CARE
OF MY BOY FIRST.

39:11.019 --> 39:15.954
THIS IS SUPER-MEDICINE,
DJANGO.

39:15.954 --> 39:18.827
IT'LL MAKE YOU BETTER.

39:18.827 --> 39:21.690
AND IT'LL PROTECT YOU
FROM KRYPTONITE.

39:26.064 --> 39:28.767
YOU'RE GONNA BE ALL RIGHT,
SWEETHEART.

39:28.767 --> 39:30.138
WE BOTH ARE.

39:42.711 --> 39:44.713
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

39:47.986 --> 39:50.388
[ SIGHS ]
GABRIEL: Luther's dead.

39:50.388 --> 39:52.721
VIRUS CONVERTED FASTER
THAN CASSIDY THOUGHT.

39:52.721 --> 39:56.625
It advanced rapidly.
He was dead in two hours.

39:58.126 --> 39:59.968
WHAT TIME IS IT?

39:59.968 --> 40:02.400
WHY?
WERE YOU SLEEPING?

40:02.400 --> 40:03.602
IT'S ONLY 8:00.

40:03.602 --> 40:05.674
WE STILL HAVE TO HAVE
OUR NIGHTLY CHECK-IN.

40:05.674 --> 40:07.035
ANNOYING, RIGHT?

40:07.035 --> 40:08.737
[ CHUCKLES ]
NOT AS ANNOYING

40:08.737 --> 40:10.679
AS HAVING YOUR ASS
SAVED BY A GIRL.

40:10.679 --> 40:13.011
YOU THINK
YOU SAVED MY ASS?

40:13.011 --> 40:14.813
WHAT ELSE IS NEW?

40:19.788 --> 40:22.891
HEY, CAN I ASK YOU
A PERSONAL QUESTION?

40:22.891 --> 40:25.654
SURE.

40:25.654 --> 40:28.527
HOW DO YOU FEEL
ABOUT THE CHIP NOW THAT...

40:28.527 --> 40:29.558
Amelia's gone?

40:29.558 --> 40:32.601
I DON'T KNOW.

40:32.601 --> 40:34.563
I'M SORRY.
I SHOULDN'T HAVE ASKED.

40:34.563 --> 40:37.566
Um, you don't need
to think about that.

40:37.566 --> 40:39.007
I THINK ABOUT IT
ALL THE TIME.

40:40.709 --> 40:41.910
GOOD NIGHT, RILEY.

40:41.910 --> 40:45.173
GOOD NIGHT.
